Package: comtrade
Title: Access and Analyse UN Comtrade International Trade Data
Version: 0.1.1
Authors@R:
    person("Charles", "Coverdale", , "charlesfcoverdale@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Download and analyse international merchandise and services trade
    data from the United Nations Comtrade database
    <https://comtradeplus.un.org/>. Retrieve bilateral trade flows, compute
    trade analytics (revealed comparative advantage, trade concentration,
    trade balance), and convert between commodity classifications
    (Harmonised System 'HS', Standard International Trade Classification
    'SITC', Broad Economic Categories 'BEC'). Covers 200+ reporter
    countries, 60+ years of goods trade data (1962-present), and services
    trade via Extended Balance of Payments Services ('EBOPS'). Works
    without registration for basic queries. A free Application Programming
    Interface ('API') key from
    <https://comtradedeveloper.un.org/> unlocks full access.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Language: en-GB
